name: Green Beaded Charm Bracelet
description:
Green Beaded Charm Bracelet

This charm bracelet has been made with an abundance of green glass beads. Each bead is individual and unique, in it's shade of green and style.

The chain is silver plated and has a flower toggle clasp and measures at 8 inches long.

This will be sent gift wrapped

name: Rockstar Charm Necklace
description:
You don't need to like rock music to wear this necklace!

The main feature is a 2 inch silver toned guiter. In addition there is a open star and a bunch of keys charm, these are also silver toned.

The chain is silver plated and is 17 inches long. It has 8 mm silver czech bohemian glass pearls and 8 mm cornflower blue faceted crystal beads .

The clasp is a silver plated lobster claw clasp.

This fab item will be sent gift wrapped.

name: Silver Charm Bracelet
description:
Silver Charm Bracelet

This unique charm bracelet has been made out of an amazing selection of silvertoned charms. 

To add a contrast, there is a row of 6mm white glass pearl beads.

As you will see from the photographs, there is a diverse selection of charms, ranging from skeleton heads to a Koala bear!

The chain is silver plated and is fitted with a flower toggle clasp and is 8 inches long.

This special bracelet is a must, if you would like own an individual, one of a kind, piece of jewellery.

It will be sent to you gift wrapped.

name: Golden Anchor Earrings
description:
Golden Anchor Earrings.

These antique bronze anchors hang from a sparkling selection of golden brown faceted crystal beads.

The beads are 6mm and have a A B rainbow-like coating, which when caught by the light, at a certain angle, makes the beads shine and glow in different colours.

The ear wires are also antique bronze.

The earrings measure 2.5 inches from top to bottom.

These earrings will be sent to you gift wrapped.

name: Starfish Crystal Set
description:
This unique starfish jewellery set will make you think of summer all year round.

I have used antique bronze starfish charms and sea blue Swarovski crystal beads to create this vision.

The starfishes measures 27x23 mm and all have a stunning sea blue Swarovski crystal, nestling beside them.

The chain is antique bronze and measures 17 inches and is fitted with a lobster claw clasp.

The earrings measure 2 1/4 inches from top to bottom and also have a sea blue Swarovski crystal. 

If you would like the crystal in a different colour, the other colours that are available are:

Red
Navy Blue
Clear
Green
Purple
Grey
Peach
 
This pretty set will be sent gift wrapped.
